# cogent reads a .env file in the working directory at startup.
# Real environment variables always take precedence over .env entries.
# A hyphen in a name is normalized to an underscore (API-KEY -> API_KEY).
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in a key. Any one of the following works:

# Generic — used for whichever provider is selected:
# API-KEY=sk-or-v1-...

# Or a provider-specific variable:
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
